system.print("=== SLOT CONTENTS ===")
system.print("")

for slot_name, slot in pairs(unit) do
    if type(slot) == "table" and slot.getClass then
        local className = slot.getClass()
        local id = slot.getLocalId()
        system.print(slot_name .. ": " .. className .. " (ID: " .. id .. ")")
        
        -- Test pattern matches
        if string.match(className, "Container%a+Group") then
            system.print("  -> MATCHES: Container%a+Group")
        end
        if string.match(className, "Container") then
            system.print("  -> MATCHES: Container (generic)")
        end
    end
end

unit.exit()
